<div data-en>

## A Brief Introduction

Hi, I'm **Albert Wang**, a Computer Science student at **Feng Chia University** in Taiwan.
I'm passionate about **embedded systems, cloud and edge computing, and AI-driven system integration**, and I enjoy building systems that truly work from the ground up.

I currently work as a **System Engineer** at [**imCloud Co., Ltd.**](https://imcloud.co/),
which is **Feng Chia University's fourth spin-off company**, originated from the **Intelligent Machines and Systems Laboratory (IMSL)**.
The company and lab were founded by **Prof. Yuan-Jen Chang**, who previously served as a visiting scholar at the [**Center for Intelligent Maintenance Systems (IMS)**](https://researchdirectory.uc.edu/facilities/85) at the **University of Cincinnati**, led by **Prof. Jay Lee**.
After returning to Taiwan, Prof. Chang introduced advanced **Predictive Health Management (PHM)** and **smart maintenance** technologies, which became the foundation for establishing both IMSL and imCloud.
My current work focuses on **software development, sensor data acquisition, PHM applications**, and **AWS Greengrass Core (GGC)** services,
where I build **data ingestion pipelines, device control logic, and IoT edge collaboration systems**.

Outside of work, I actively explore various **side projects**, especially with **Raspberry Pi** and **ESP32**.
I'm a dedicated **DietPi** user, often experimenting with lightweight systems for server deployment, automation, and edge computing integration.

I'm also preparing for my next academic step — pursuing a **master's degree abroad** in **Canada** or the **United States**,
focusing on **AI, data analytics, and predictive maintenance (PHM)**.
To achieve that, I'm improving my English proficiency, aiming to reach **IELTS 6 / CEFR B2** within a year.

Beyond programming, I'm passionate about **flight simulation (VATSIM Callsign: EVA431)**, **photography**, and **amateur radio communication (BX7ADG)**.

I'm also building my personal brand **Prisvalis**, with the domain [**prisvalis.com**](https://prisvalis.com).
Although it's still in its early stage, my goal is to turn it into a platform that integrates **AI, data, and automation**,
developing technologies that truly make a difference in everyday life.

